  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK965">
<l>kuṉṟi ṉaṉaiyāruṅ kuṉṟuvar kuṉṟuva </l>
<l>kuṉṟi yaṉaiya ceyiṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even those who are exalted like a hill will be thought low, if they commit deeds that are debasing.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
